high_descs: Turn around and then left and right to locate the sink.
Pick up the potato from inside the sink.
Carry the potato and turn around, then left to locate the microwave.
Open the microwave and place the potato inside. Shut the door and then open it. Take the potato out and shut the door.
Carry the potato and turn around. Turn right and move to the far counter.
Place the potato on the counter, all the way to the right.
anns.task_desc: Heat a potato and place it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around then walk forward and left to the kitchen sink
Pick up the potato out of the sink
Turn around and walk across the room to the microwave in the corner
Heat the potato in the microwave then remove it
Turn around and walk forward and left to the small dark table left of the kitchen sink
Put the potato on the table
anns.task_desc: Put the cooked potato on the small table

high_descs: Turn around and walk across the room to face the sink.
Pick up the potato in the sink.
Turn around, walk to the table, then turn left and walk forward to face the microwave.
Heat the potato in the microwave and then remove it.
Turn around and walk across the room, then turn right and walk forward to face the black table.
Place the potato on the black table.
anns.task_desc: To heat a potato as well as place it on the black table.
